<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>363</hymn_number>
<title>RAWL TUANTU A PUMH HNA CH363</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Sunparnak ram in hlasak na thei maw? Lawmhnak hlasak na thei maw?
 Lungtho tein kan faphal pum u si, A donghnak caan a phan deng cang,

[C1]
   Rawltuan uktu Bawipa a ra deng cang, Aan dawh hmaipanh cu kan hmuh
   cang lai, Rawltuan uktu Bawipa a ra deng cang, Rawltuan tu a pumh hna lai.

[V2]
 Kan dawtmi hna nih, sunparnak ram in, Lunglawm in an run kan zoh, An
 rian an lim i harnak an lonh cang, Kamhmi sui luchin an hmuh cang,

[C2]
   Rawltuan uktu Bawipa a ra deng cang, Aan dawh hmaipanh cu kan hmuh
   cang lai, Rawltuan uktu Bawipa a ra deng cang, Rawltuan tu a pumh hna lai.

[V3]
 Sunparnak ram in hladawh a rung thang, Kan lung thin cu a thawnter, Cu
 hla aw dawh nih nunnak a thanter, Ni lin tang rian kan tuan lioah,

[C3]
   Rawltuan uktu Bawipa a ra deng cang, Aan dawh hmaipanh cu kan hmuh
   cang lai, Rawltuan uktu Bawipa a ra deng cang, Rawltuan tu a pumh hna lai.

[V4]
 Sunparnak ram in hla dawh a rung thang; Lawmhnak le par dawh enhnak, A
 nungmi zumhnak thawngin kan hngalh cang, Kannih zong kan sa ti hna lai.

[C4]
   Rawltuan uktu Bawipa a ra deng cang, Aan dawh hmaipanh cu kan hmuh
   cang lai, Rawltuan uktu Bawipa a ra deng cang, Rawltuan tu a pumh hna lai.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
</song>